quran[96]{c,v,t}:
  56,1,Si darotoongal ngal darike
  56,2,alanaa daragol maggal ngol fennoowo
  56,3,"Hoyfin…óinayngal (yeddu…ďe), …ďamtayngal (gom…óim…ďe)"
  56,4,Si leydi ndin dilliniraama dillannde
  56,5,pelle …óen munciroyee muncannde
  56,6,…óe wonta collaari ruuynayndi
  56,7,wattinon nooneeji tati
  56,8,Ko wontiroo…ďe √Īaamo …ďen - iskin …ďen yim…ďe √Īaamo
  56,9,"e wontiroo…ďe nano …ďen, bis e …ďen yim…ďe nano"
  56,10,"Ko adondiraynoo…ďe …ďen (e mo∆ī∆īere ka aduna), adoytee (naadeede Aljanna)"
  56,11,Ko …ďen woni badnitaa…ďe …ďen
  56,12,ka Aljannaaji neeminii…ói
  56,13,"dental jeyaangal e [mofte] adinoo…ďe …ďen"
  56,14,"e see…óaa…ďe jeyaa…ďe e [mofte] sakkitii…ďe …ďen"
  56,15,"hi…ďe e hoore dan…óe yu…ď…ďiraa…óe [kaŇčŇče]"
  56,16,"hara hi…ďe so…ď…ďindii e majje, fewtondir…ďe"
  56,17,Sukaa…ďe duuminaa…ďe hino wanngoo hakkunde ma…ď…ďe
  56,18,"wonndude e √Īeddu…óe, e cataloy, e koroy e [hebbiniraakoy] beere ilaynde"
  56,19,"…ďe muusetaake ko*e nder ton, …ďe siwritaa"
  56,20,e muuyantee…ói …ói …ďe su…ďotoo
  56,21,e teewu colli ngu …ďe tuuyatee
  56,22,e huurul'aynii…ďe -yaaja gite en
  56,23,nanndu…ďe e kaŇčŇče lu'lu'u maraa…óe
  56,24,njo…ďdi ko …ďe gollaynoo kon
  56,25,"∆Āe nanataa nder ton haala meere, wanaa ko bakkondiŇčta"
  56,26,"si wanaa wi'aneede : \"Salaaman! Salaaman!\" [Sa…ói mon! sa…ói mon]"
  56,27,"E wontiroo…ďe √Īaamo …ďen, ko woni …ďen yim…ďe √Īaamo"
  56,28,"[∆Āe wonay] e le…ó…óe jaa…ďe new…óu…óe"
  56,29,e banaanaje fawandir…óe
  56,30,e …óowdi duumiindi
  56,31,e ndiyam juuray…óam
  56,32,e …ďi…ó…ďe le…ó…óe …óuu…óu…óe
  56,33,…óe ta∆īondirtaa …óe ha…óetaake
  56,34,e dan…óe …ďamtaa…óe
  56,35,Ko Menen tagi fu…ó…ói …ďe
  56,36,Men wa…ói …ďe curbaa…ďe-boomi
  56,37,"yi…óu…ďe wor…ďe mun, goree…ďe"
  56,38,"[Men marani …ďe] yim…ďe √Īaamo …ďen"
  56,39,"Dental jeyaa…ďe e [mofte] adinoo…ďe …ďen"
  56,40,"e see…óaa…ďe jeyaa…ďe e [mofte] sakkitii…ďe …ďen"
  56,41,E wontiroo…ďe nano …ďen. Ko hom…ďe woni …ďen yim…ďe nano
  56,42,"[∆Āen] no e nguleendi e fatay…óam"
  56,43,e …óowdi curki …ďawluki
  56,44,"wonaa …ďuu…ďundi, wanaa teddundi"
  56,45,"Ado …óum, hari ko …ďe neeminaa…ďe"
  56,46,…ďe laatino hi…ďe deppitoo e bakkaat maw…ói …óin
  56,47,"hi…ďe wi'aynoo: \"Enee, si men maayii, men wontii mbullaari e ∆īi'e, hara ko men immintinoytee…ďe"
  56,48,hay baabiraa…ďe amen adinoo…ďe …ďen
  56,49,"Maaku : \"Pellet, aram…ďe e sakkitii…ďe"
  56,50,ko moo…ďoytee…ďe e √Īalaande anndaande waqutu mun
  56,51,"refti pellet, onon …ďee majju…ďe fennu…ďe [ummital]"
  56,52,"ko on nyaamoyay…ďe e leggal \"Zaqquumi\" ngal"
  56,53,ngal hebbiniroyton deedi
  56,54,yariron ngal kadi fatay…óam
  56,55,yariron wa yarugol ngelooba …óom…óaamba
  56,56,Ko …óum woni ko …ďe kottiigu !u! en √Īalnde njo…ďdi diina
  56,57,"Ko Menen woni ko tagi on. Ha…ói goonginon [Men immintinay on]"
  56,58,On yi'ii on maniiyu mo rufoton
  56,59,"Ko onon tagata mo? Kaa ko Menen woni tagoo…ďe […óum]"
  56,60,Ko Menen hoddiri maayde nden hakkunde mon. Men wonaali adatee…ďe
  56,61,"e wattitugol yeruu…ďe mon, Men fu…ó…óira on e ko on anndah"
  56,62,Gom…óii hi…óon anndi tageede aranun …óum. Ko ha…ói waajito…óon
  56,63,On yi'ii kon ko remoton
  56,64,Ko onon fu…óinta …óum? Kaa ko Menen woni fu…óinoo…ďe …ďen
  56,65,"Si Men haajuno, pellet, Men wa…óayno ndu foron. Wattinon hi…óon haawoo [wi'a]"
  56,66,Menen ko men leptetee…ďe perte ko min nafqi ko
  56,67,wurin ko men ha…óaa…ďe
  56,68,On yi'ii ndiyam …óam yaroton …óam
  56,69,"E ko onon jippiniri …óam ka duule? Kaa ko Menen jippini […óam]"
  56,70,"Si Men haajuno, Men wa…óayno …óam kaa…ó…óam. Ko ha…ói yetton [Allah]"
  56,71,On yi'ii yiite nge hu…ď…ďoton ngen
  56,72,"E ko onon woodini wa…ói le…ó…óe mum? Kaa ko Menen woodini […óe]"
  56,73,"Men wa…óir ngen [yiite] waaju, e nafitor nge setotoo…ďe"
  56,74,"Subbunhinor innde Joomi maa, Maw…óo On"
  56,75,Mi woondirii mutir…óe koode …óen
  56,76,"Pellet, …óum ko woondoore mawnde, si hi…óon anndunoo"
  56,77,Pellet ndee ko Alqur'aanaare konde teddunde
  56,78,wonnde e deftere reenaande
  56,79,meemataa nden si wanaa la…ď…ďinaa…ďe …ďen
  56,80,ko jippiniraande ka Jey…óo Winndere nden
  56,81,E ko ndee yewtere wonki ko pennoton onon
  56,82,"Hi…óon wa…óa arsike mon (to…ďo ngon) ko on fennoo…ďe [arsiku…óo On]"
  56,83,Ko ha…óata nde wonkii yottii ka looko∆īere
  56,84,hara onon hi…óon ndaara ontuma
  56,85,"hara non ko Menen …ďuri on …ďadaade mo, kono on yi'ataa"
  56,86,"Ko ha…óata on, si tawiino hara on warjetaake"
  56,87,"rutton kin [wonkii], si tawii ko on goongu…ďe"
  56,88,Si tawii on ko jeyaa…óo e …ďattinaa…ďe …ďen
  56,89,"haray ko fowtere, e mo∆ī∆īere, e Aljannaaji neema (woodani mo)"
  56,90,Si tawii kadi ko jeyaa…óo e yim…ďe √Īaamo …ďen
  56,91,"haray [o ja…ď…ďoroyte] : \"Kisal maa\" e …ďaŇčge yim…ďe √Īaamo …ďen"
  56,92,Si tawii non ko jeyanoo…óo e fennu…ďe majju…ďe …ďen
  56,93,haray ho…ótorde makko on ko fatay…óam
  56,94,e sumeede Jahiimi
  56,95,"Pellet, ko …óum woni goonga yananaa…óo on"
  56,96,"Subbunhinor innde Joomi maa, Maw…óo On"